summary: Guys I’m emotional...
body:
Guys I’m emotional…

…a little over a year ago we knew NOTHING about TS6, and now we’re at the end of the reputation tour. Think of how far we’ve come. The social media perge. The end of the drought. Taking back the narrative. Thousands of Meet&Greets. Encouraging us to vote. The Delicate music video. The high note in Don’t Blame Me. Long Live performed every night in 2018.

It’s been one hell of a ride. Here’s to this GORGEOUS fandom I’m proud to be apart of.🥂
